and this is one of the most common decorators you'll be using, besides the component decorator of course

3
00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:15.990
because it allows you to communicate with your component from outside, through attributes or by directly

4
00:00:15.990 --> 00:00:18.210
setting the properties.

5
00:00:18.230 --> 00:00:25.140
One important note, when you do set the property as we did here in this line, you know this because I also

6
